The paper deals with privacy and security in messaging systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also introduces new techniques and optimizations for server-side storage and performance, which could fall under the categories of data structures (cs.DS), distributed computing (cs.DC), databases (cs.DB), and machine learning (cs.LG).
